ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
SubjectTransfer of Duties Order
PrecisOrder transferring from (1) the Department of Health to the Department of Indigenous Services Canada the control and supervision of that portion of the federal public administration in the Department of Health known as the First Nations and Inuit Health Branch; and(2) the Department of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to the Department of Indigenous Services Canada the control and supervision of those portions of the federal public administration known as the Education and Social Development Programs and Partnership Sector, and the Regional Operations Sector.
